The species included in 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Sphaerodoridae" genus="Clavodorum" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Clavodorum" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">Clavodorum</taxonomicName>
